{
  "stem": "24830.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They never came out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in the beginning, they were not very good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, they were starting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But after, they became very, very good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the first thing, I have to change my name.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So I had very good paper.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like, my name became Micheline Beaumont.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the person I have the name-- actually, they was out of France.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you know, I have a completely different background.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was born, I think, in Grenoble, or something like this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I have a baptise certificate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And what you have to-- you have to have a card for everything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to have a card to eat-- food card, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] tobacco card.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't smoke, anyway.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So all this little-- well first, the people who work got the best paper.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But [FRENCH]-- that was-- that was my work, actually, and the work of all these people working with me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "To save people means to find-- change their paper, find them a hiding place, and give them all these paper.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then all these young people went all-- all over the country to find hiding place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I didn't make it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whoever was in charge made it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, well they were-- they started.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- but they became very sophisticated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like they-- around the [FRENCH], they could move the letter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we went to a-- you know, we have to get stamp, you know, what you apply.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we have to get stamp from all over the country.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the best place to get stamp-- if-- if a town has been bombarded, and was destroyed, that was very good.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they couldn't check.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then a lot of-- I mean, a lot of French people were collaborator.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
